gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Heat 114, Warriors 102
gameRecap.excerpt: The Heat defeated the Warriors, 114-102. Tyler Herro led the way with 26 points, seven rebounds, and two assists for the Heat, with Bam Adebayo adding 17 points and 11 rebounds in the victory. Stephen Curry tallied 13 points, five assists, and four rebounds for the Warriors in the losing effort. The Heat improve to 19-12 in the regular season, while the Warriors fall to 15-16.
